---
import { Email } from '@/components/email';
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/main-layout.astro';
---

<MainLayout pageTitle="Refund Policy" variant="legal">
  <h1 class="text-center">Refund Policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: Jul 1, 2024</p>

  <p>
    This Refund Policy outlines the terms and conditions under which refunds may
    be requested for services provided by Mrugesh Mohapatra Co.
  </p>

  <h2>Services Covered</h2>
  <p>
    This refund policy applies to all consulting, development, and professional
    services provided by Mrugesh Mohapatra Co., including but not limited to:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Software development services</li>
    <li>Cloud infrastructure consulting</li>
    <li>Technical consulting sessions</li>
    <li>Code reviews and audits</li>
    <li>Training and educational services</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Refund Eligibility</h2>
  <p>Refunds may be considered under the following circumstances:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Service was not delivered as specified in the agreement</li>
    <li>Significant delays due to our fault without prior notification</li>
    <li>Technical issues on our end that prevent service delivery</li>
    <li>
      Cancellation request made within 24 hours of initial payment (for
      consulting sessions)
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Non-Refundable Services</h2>
  <p>The following are generally not eligible for refunds:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Completed consulting sessions or meetings</li>
    <li>Custom development work that has been delivered and accepted</li>
    <li>Services where work has already commenced</li>
    <li>Cancellations made less than 24 hours before scheduled sessions</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Refund Process</h2>
  <p>To request a refund:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Contact us at <Email /> with your refund request</li>
    <li>Provide your order/invoice number and reason for the refund</li>
    <li>Allow 5-7 business days for review of your request</li>
    <li>If approved, refunds will be processed within 10 business days</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Partial Refunds</h2>
  <p>
    In cases where work has been partially completed, partial refunds may be
    considered based on the percentage of work completed and delivered.
  </p>

  <h2>Payment Method</h2>
  <p>
    Refunds will be processed using the same payment method used for the
    original transaction. Processing times may vary depending on your bank or
    payment provider.
  </p>

  <h2>Dispute Resolution</h2>
  <p>
    If you're not satisfied with our refund decision, we encourage you to reach
    out to discuss the matter further. We're committed to finding fair solutions
    for all parties involved.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact Information</h2>
  <p>
    For refund requests or questions about this policy, please contact us at <Email
    />.
  </p>

  <h2>Policy Changes</h2>
  <p>
    We reserve the right to update this refund policy at any time. Changes will
    be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.
  </p>
</MainLayout>
